{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01RzvB7YLbv7oHe8QimNbemj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fixed issue #19 — added chunked/streaming processing for large audio files:\n\n- Added `split_chunks` and `join_chunks` methods to `AudioBuffer` with overlap-add crossfading\n- Pipeline automatically switches to chunked mode when file exceeds 5M samples (~60s at 44.1kHz)\n- Processes in ~30-second chunks with 1-second overlap regions\n- Crossfade blending at chunk boundaries prevents audible artifacts\n- Original buffer is dropped before chunk processing to reduce peak memory usage\n\n```\n---RALPH_STATUS---\nSTATUS: COMPLETE\nTASKS_COMPLETED_THIS_LOOP: 1\nFILES_MODIFIED: 2\nTESTS_STATUS: PASSING\nWORK_TYPE: IMPLEMENTATION\nEXIT_SIGNAL: false\nRECOMMENDATION: Next task: #1 - Add spectrogram visualization for cleaned audio (GUI)\n---END_RALPH_STATUS---\n```"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":304,"cache_read_input_tokens":120368,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":304},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9bd7957-c8f2-4e48-8fcc-7059d242854c","uuid":"b45ec0a0-35e7-4f08-a4b6-4c8d0a065d40"}
